    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏介绍</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款以练习打字能力为目标的生存射击游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演一个末日炮台，通过输入敌人身上对应的字母来消灭敌人</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击杀靠近你的一切敌人并尽可能的生存更长的时间来获得更高的评分</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063740/extras/9b574e18d7435fbec3d7fc3f9c59138a.poster.avif?t=1766462687\" width=652 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063740/extras/9b574e18d7435fbec3d7fc3f9c59138a.webm?t=1766462687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063740/extras/9b574e18d7435fbec3d7fc3f9c59138a.mp4?t=1766462687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏目前已包含经典模式和道具模式</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经典模式是为了锻炼打字能力而打造的纯硬核竞技模式</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >道具模式则是可以通过升级来获得道具的娱乐模式</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在道具模式中，你可以组合你需要的技能并最大化他们的作用来生存更久并获得更多的得分</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063740/extras/db438bbba14bf9c1b9e654636ee872dd.poster.avif?t=1766462687\" width=652 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063740/extras/db438bbba14bf9c1b9e654636ee872dd.webm?t=1766462687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063740/extras/db438bbba14bf9c1b9e654636ee872dd.mp4?t=1766462687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>你是否是世界最强的打字选手之一？来试试这款打字生存射击游戏吧，在不断练习中不断变强，最终你会证明你自己。</p>",
